com.example.mooderation.auth.base

Class AuthenticationResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.example.mooderation.auth.base.AuthenticationResult

  • public class AuthenticationResult
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains the results of an authentication query. The query is either a success, in which case the authentication credentials may be obtained using getSuccess(), or a failure, in which case the error may be obtained using getFailure().
